name: Dirty Dozer
overview: You are Rusty, an old dozer who avoids his retirement ... and,as long as you do your job well, you will avoid becoming junk.Your mission: simple, move the boxes to their place. It is an easy task, but it has its own dangers: wandering electric shocks, cannons, presses, etc. and please don't get stuck. Sometimes you have to clear the way to the box, and you will have to break brick walls and plan your movements carefully.Good luck! Rusty you will need it.
